<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3241198>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–21. Elathous agilis sp. nov. 13—male, holotype, dorsal view; 14—male, holotype, lateral view; 15—female, paratype, dorsal view; 16—female, paratype, pronotum; 17—male, holotype, antennomeres; 18—female, paratype, antennomeres. E. lizleri Mertlik, 2005 female, holotype. 19—antennomeres; 20—dorsal view; 21—pronotum. Scale bars=1.0 mm (Figs 16–19, 21), 2.0 mm (Figs 13–15, 20)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3241198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3241200>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–30. Elathous agilis sp. nov. pregenital segments and genitalia. Male, holotype. 22—abdominal tergite VIII; 23—abdominal tergite IX & X; 24—abdominal sternite VIII; 25—abdominal sternite IX; 26—aedeagus; Female, paratype. 27—abdominal tergite VII; 28—abdominal tergite VIII; 29—abdominal sternite VIII; 30—ovipositor. Scale bars=0.5 mm (Figs 22–28), 1.0 mm (Figs 29–30)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3241200/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3241212>
    dc:description "FIGURES 69–71. 69—Habitat of Elathous agilis sp. nov. at Horsh Arz el-Rab. 70—Living larva of Elathous agilis sp. nov. at Horsh Arz el-Rab, in white-rotten Cedrus log. 71—Living larva of Elathous agilis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3241212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

